{"tid":2120990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（韓天堂）朝中貿易減7成陷飢荒 北韓金正恩建議人民吃烏龜","createTime":"2020-07-23T04:42:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T09:46:43.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"212cc935391633d323dd9ec4ce652641876306e0","tid":2120990,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:42:54.000Z","msg":"北韓在國際上受到各國的制裁，又因為武漢肺炎關係，北韓從1月下旬，為阻斷疫情傳播已下令關閉平壤邊境，因此與中國之間的貿易往來，從今年1月到5月已下降7成，少了民生經濟高度依賴的中國，北韓國內開始鬧飢荒，北韓最高領導人金正恩為此制定了一套「營養政策」，建議民眾可以吃烏龜或吃減肥藥產生飽足感...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/vJWh.JyEX8zMj9z2HiyhdA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQ4MA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/qTjfZW3E7kf9635kRC_Jlg--~B/aD0xNDQwO3c9MTkyMDtzbT0xO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cmmedia.com.tw/3349e37f235a7363effd674c349bb647\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FvJWh.JyEX8zMj9z2HiyhdA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQ4MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FqTjfZW3E7kf9635kRC_Jlg--~B%2FaD0xNDQwO3c9MTkyMDtzbT0xO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fcmmedia.com.tw%2F3349e37f235a7363effd674c349bb647&h=63b68281&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖片來源／Pixabay）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/中朝貿易減7成陷飢荒-北韓金正恩建議民眾吃烏龜-軍隊養兔來吃-013219984.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%9D%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%B8%9B7%E6%88%90%E9%99%B7%E9%A3%A2%E8%8D%92-%E5%8C%97%E9%9F%93%E9%87%91%E6%AD%A3%E6%81%A9%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%BE%E5%90%83%E7%83%8F%E9%BE%9C-%E8%BB%8D%E9%9A%8A%E9%A4%8A%E5%85%94%E4%BE%86%E5%90%83-013219984.html&d=DosFxDX7yTzXLN9Gri3QgNMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=61bb5ce9\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/中朝貿易減7成陷飢荒-北韓金正恩建議民眾吃烏龜-軍隊養兔來吃-013219984.html</a>"},{"pid":"c44e0df9bb57b588e1bf1c73237ddd41762d6694","tid":2120990,"uid":7323,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07